            <![CDATA[
            <h3>Version 1.7.36 - Expiry Date Auto-Disable/Enable Logic</h3>

            <h4>New Features</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>When expiry date is set to a past date, company is automatically disabled and all tokens suspended</li>
                <li>When expiry date is changed from past to future/never, company is re-enabled and tokens unsuspended</li>
                <li>This works both from the UI (immediately on save) and via scheduled task (every 6 hours)</li>
            </ul>

            <h4>Previous Versions</h4>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>v1.7.35:</strong> Fixed timezone in expiry date picker (UTC handling)</li>
                <li><strong>v1.7.34:</strong> Fixed context validation in session APIs</li>
                <li><strong>v1.7.33:</strong> Added missing get_company_id_from_token() method</li>
            </ul>
